0.1003 2012.12.10
    - Added Test::PodSpelling to dist.ini and fixed spelling errors.
    - Replaced is_deeply() tests with ok() for arrayrefs.

0.1002 2012.03.25
    - Removed Imager write test.

0.1001 2012.03.21
